■ Introduction

Unfettered access to onchain data

No more reliance on multiple centralized sources. Covalent Network offers decentralized means of accessing onchain data, whether it's running nodes, pulling data directly to your database, or simply querying the API.

Chains we support

We support onchain data for over 200 blockchains, including Ethereum, Binance Smart Chain, Polygon, Avalanche, and more.
■ Long-Term Data Availability

The Ethereum Wayback Machine

Today’s financial economy is onchain, but Ethereum data is more like a billboard than permanent storage, this is solved with Long-Term Data Availability via the Ethereum Wayback Machine.
■ RUN EWM

EWM Light Client

A Lightweight Solution to Spot Audit the Validity of Data on the Ethereum Wayback Machine.

Covalent Powered Products

■ API

GoldRush

GoldRush is a set of data tools that enable easy web3 development across 200+ blockchains. Powered by Covalent, GoldRush offers structured onchain data through powerful SDKs, APIs, UI Kits, Decoders and templates.
■ Data Analytics

Increment

Increment allows you to query and visualize the complete historical dataset of 200+ blockchains, including every smart contract, event, transaction, and block. Powered by Covalent, Increment brings SQL based analytics to web3.
